summary: Why investors should use the Zacks Earnings ESP tool to help find stocks that are poised to top quarterly earnings estimates.

headline: 2 Consumer Stocks for Long-Term Investors and 1 to Question
summary: Retailers are adapting their business models as technology changes how people shop. Still, demand can be volatile as the industry is exposed to the ups and downs of consumer spending. This has stirred some uncertainty lately as retail stocks have tumbled by 11.8% over the past six months. This drop was worse than the S&P 500’s 2% fall.
